@node Future "xPlay 1.1 - Future"

@{FG shine}Future enhancements@{FG text}
-------------------

    - Support ATAK and RLSE chunks

    - Support CHAN and PAN chunks

    - Ability to play Fibonacci-delta-encoded IFF-Samples
      (Unlikely - xpk is better supported, and not lossy)

    - Ability to play Exponential-delta-encoded IFF-Samples
      (Unlikely - xpk is better supported, and not lossy)

    - Workbench AppIcon for Playing Samples
      (Unlikely - use toolmanager or something)

    - Commodity with embedded UPD-Emulation
      (Does anyone still use upd?)
@endnode

